OL,5, A Ryanair boss has criticised airports 
OL,6, for not recruiting enough staff to     
OL,7, cater for the rebound in travellers,   
OL,8, saying they had "had one job to do to".
OL,10,FNeil Sorahan, chief financial officer, 
OL,11,Fsaid "various governments" and airports
OL,12,Fneeded to be held to account for "not  
OL,13,Fstaffing up appropriately".            
OL,15,FHis comments come as staff shortages at
OL,16,Fairports have led to major disruption  
OL,17,Fand cancellations in recent months.    
OL,19,FAirports said they had been recruiting 
OL,20,Fsecurity staff since late last year.   
